+	 * unconditionally xa_destroy() regardless of MR mode. Explicit MRs
+	 * never touch this xarray, so it stays empty for them. The xarray
+	 * allocator is invoked under GFP_KERNEL on the cmpxchg insertion
+	 * path below.
